high_descs: turn around and move forward to the counter that is to the left of the stove
pick up the butter knife that is directly in front of the tan bowl
turn to the left and at the end of the counter on the left turn left and stop to face the black trash can that is at the end of the counter
slice the green apple that is in the trash can with the knife
put the knife in to the trash can behind the apples
remove a slice of the green apple from the trash can
turn to the left and at the edge of the counter, turn to the right and move forward to the stove on the left, turn left to face the stove with the microwave above it
open the microwave door, put the apple slice in to the microwave, close the door, cook for a few seconds, open the door, remove the apple slice and close the door
turn to the right and move to the edge of the counter on the right, turn right and move to the center of the counter turning right to face the counter long ways
put the apple slice on to the counter
anns.task_desc: put a cooked apple slice on to the counter

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the wall, hang a right and go to the counter to the left of the stove where the lettuce is.
Pick up the butter knife that is in front of the bowl on the counter.
Turn to the left, go to the end of the counter and turn left, go to the garbage can that will be on the left.
Cut the apple that is in the garbage can into slices.
Put the knife in the garbage can.
Pick up a slice of apple that is in the garbage can.
Turn to the left, go to the fridge, hang a right and go to the microwave that is above the stove on the left.
Put the apple in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the cooked apple from the microwave.
Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a right and go to the counter where the plant is that is on the left.
Put the slice of apple on the counter to the right of the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked apple slice on a counter.

high_descs: Go to the left of the stove
Take a knife from the counter
Go to the bin
Cut an apple in the bin
Put the knife in the bin
Take an apple piece
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple
Go to the kitchen island
Put the apple down on the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple slice on the kitchen island
